text: Primorye () is the name of several inhabited localities in Russia: *Primorye, Kaliningrad Oblast, an urban locality (an urban-type settlement) in Svetlogorsky District of Kaliningrad Oblast *Primorye, Perm Krai, a rural locality (a village) in Chastinsky District of Perm Krai ==See also== *Primorsky Krai, a federal subject of Russia informally known as Primorye *Primorsk (disambiguation) *Primorsky (disambiguation) ==References== ja:プリモリェ ru:Приморье (значения)
title: Primorye (inhabited locality)
